data.name: label213.Text
data.value: This pack of server tools is a free distribution, and is also codenamed ToPAST (Tales of Pirates Admin Server Tools). This pack contains GM tools, Admin tools, SQL/Server settings, Calculators, Item Editors, script ijectors, Auto Editors, and more! The Administrators have the ability to make new accounts and characters with ease, and they can transfer characters with a flick. This has been developed to attempt to get rid of the old privatia server "Webserver" server tools, and make a new revolution.

data.name: label215.Text
data.value: The GM Server acts like a proxy in which you can get data from the database remotely without opening a huge hole in your server's security. It also has the login credentials of GM Users. Also, set to default, you have a Background AES256-SHA security system. (This may effect speed) Also a few things might be added to it, like being able to prevent a client from connecting (Kicking), and running macro-commands. (Such as "RemoveAllOldUsers") Please Note: When you log in, any pending SQL Connections will be abandoned.
